short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Displays info on the anime that an osu! beatmap is from

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds an extra section under the osu! beatmap info with information regarding the anime the song is from. This extension uses anilist.co to display information such as the title, cover art, year of release, average rating and tags.
